25 (a) Mandatory initial and continuing training requirements for all SANE
26 nurses providing services in the state, ensuring that trauma-informed and
27 evidence-based protocols are integrated into all education and practice settings.
28 (b) A statewide preceptor network, aligned with existing and available best
29 practice guidelines from both national and state organizations.
